<browser-action actionType="BrowserCaptureWebVitals" isHit="false"
    name="Capture Web Vitals" uid="d9ad35e5-601d-41f5-8719-de8a5e9815a5">
    <description>Captures Core Web Vitals metrics during Virtual User navigation. This helps detect performance issues that affect the user experience.

NeoLoad collects the following metrics for each defined URL:

- Largest Contentful Paint (LCP)
- Interaction to Next Paint (INP)
- Cumulative Layout Shift (CLS)

If you don't define a URL, NeoLoad aggregates metrics across all visited pages.

To collect all metrics, place this action before the first Navigate action. The Virtual User needs to stay a minimum amount of time and perform at least one interaction to ensure Web Vitals were collected for a given page.
Possible parameters are:&#xd;
- url (optional): A url (excluding query parameters) to group Web Vitals metrics data under.</description>
    <custom-action-parameter name="url" type="TEXT" value="https://samples.azuremaps.com/"/>
    <custom-action-parameter name="url" type="TEXT" value="https://samples.azuremaps.com/animations/animate-a-gps-trace"/>
